name: Abstract Generative Painting 3/6
description: A series of six generative paintings explore the relationship between the machine and the artist, contributing to the beauty of the final piece.  The process began by painting abstract strokes on paper, scanned them and imported into the 3D software as 'normal map' textures. The artwork is randomly generated by the software creating unique and different compositions. 2020  Acrylic and generative JPG, 3507 x 4960 px
